The counts table to the left can be used to filter the Faults table below. **Select a fault, right-click, and choose cross-filter.**

Notes

Telemetry should have been "fixed" (PII removed) after:
- vscode-fabric-0.3.25
- vscode-fabric-appdev-0.3.21

TODO

Auth errors are currently filtered out due to bug [1334540](https://powerbi.visualstudio.com/AppDev/_workitems/edit/1334540)

tiles.title: DataDev extension activation performance over time
Notes
tiles.markdownText:
This page queries VSCode telemetry, not VSCode extension telemetry.
Thus we can't filter on VSCode extension version. As fixes propagate to users, their incidence will decrease

tiles.title: New tile
tiles.markdownText:
Enter text in [markdown](https://github.github.com/gfm/) format

Note: if editing this dashboard (or any dashboard) be aware that an intervening update (by you or anybody) will render your edits useless. There is no versioning and synchronizing is minimal.

Permissions:

        DevDiv Data Readers CoreIdentity - Manage Entitlement https://coreidentity.microsoft.com/manage/Entitlement/entitlement/devdivdatare-gaqs

        PBI C and AI diag access CoreIdentity - Manage Entitlement https://coreidentity.microsoft.com/manage/Entitlement/entitlement/pbicandaidia-zpow

Wiki page to use a RAID to get logs https://dev.azure.com/powerbi/AppDev/_wiki/wikis/AppDev.wiki/122427/How-to-trace-a-RAID-Request-Activity-ID-using-Fabric-Service-Portal-Trace-Viewer

Wiki page to decode redacted VSCode callstacks https://dev.azure.com/powerbi/AppDev/_wiki/wikis/AppDev.wiki/122439/Decode-VSCode-callstack-shows-in-Telemetry

GDPR Classifcation page: https://gdpr.datasmart.ms/?q=entityname%20like%20%27fabric.vscode-fabric%25%27

Known Issues for Fabric Extensions: https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-fabric/issues

queries.text:
_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/activation"
| summarize count() by endofday(ServerTimestamp)

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"
| extend ErrorMessage = tostring(Properties['errormessage'])
| where ErrorMessage != "auth-error" // https://powerbi.visualstudio.com/AppDev/_workitems/edit/1334540
| summarize ['Workspaces errors']=count() by startofday(ClientTimestamp)

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"
| extend ErrorMessage = tostring(Properties['errormessage'])
| where ErrorMessage != "auth-error" // https://powerbi.visualstudio.com/AppDev/_workitems/edit/1334540
| extend Source = tostring(Properties['source'])
| extend Action = tostring(Properties['action'])
| extend Fault = tostring(Properties['fault'])
| where isempty(['_fault']) or Fault == ['_fault'] // Freetext filtering
| extend ExceptionStack = tostring(Properties['exceptionstack'])
| extend errcodeq = extract('.*errorCode":"(.*?")', 1, ExceptionStack, typeof(string))
| extend  ErrorCode = iff(errcodeq == '', extract('(\\A.*)', 1, ExceptionStack, typeof(string)), substring(errcodeq, 0, strlen(errcodeq)-1))
| project ClientTimestamp, ExtensionVersion, ErrorMessage, Fault,ErrorCode, ExceptionStack, Source, Action, VSCodeSessionId, VSCodeVersion, Platform, PlatformVersion, Properties
| order by ClientTimestamp desc

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric-appdev" or ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric-functions"
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"
| summarize ['AppDev errors']=count() by startofday(ClientTimestamp)

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric-functions"
| where EventName =="fabric.vscode-fabric-functions/extension/error"
| extend ErrorMessage = tostring(Properties['errormessage'])
| extend Source = tostring(Properties['source'])
| extend Action = tostring(Properties['action'])
| extend Fault = tostring(Properties['fault'])
| where Properties ['common.extensionmode'] == 1
| where isempty(['_fault']) or Fault == ['_fault'] // Freetext filtering
| extend ExceptionStack = tostring(Properties['exceptionstack'])
| project ClientTimestamp, ExtensionVersion, ErrorMessage, Fault, ExceptionStack, Source, Action, VSCodeVersion, Platform, VSCodeSessionId, Properties
| order by ClientTimestamp desc

_events
| summarize dcount(VSCodeSessionId) by endofday(ServerTimestamp)

_events
| where EventName has "activation"
| project format_datetime(startofday(ServerTimestamp), "yyyy-MM-dd"), ExtensionName, ExtensionVersion, VSCodeSessionId, IsMicrosoftInternal,  VSCodeVersion, Platform, PlatformVersion, GeoCity, GeoCountryRegionIso,  VSCodeMachineId, Properties, Measures
| order by ServerTimestamp desc, VSCodeSessionId, ExtensionName desc

_events
| summarize dcount(VSCodeSessionId) by Platform

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/create"
| project-reorder EventName, Properties, Measures, ExtensionVersion
| summarize count() by startofday(ServerTimestamp)

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
//| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/extension/error"
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"

| where ErrorMessage != "auth-error" // https://powerbi.visualstudio.com/AppDev/_workitems/edit/1334540
| extend Source = tostring(Properties['source'])
| extend Action = tostring(Properties['action'])
| extend Fault = tostring(Properties['fault'])
| extend ExceptionStack = tostring(Properties['exceptionstack'])
// | project ClientTimestamp, ExtensionVersion, ErrorMessage, Fault, ExceptionStack, Source, Action, VSCodeVersion, Platform, PlatformVersion, Properties
// | order by ClientTimestamp desc
| summarize count() by Fault
| order by count_ desc 
| project-reorder count_

_events

| summarize count() by startofday(ServerTimestamp)

_events
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/load-items"
| extend Result = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| where not(Result)
| extend Fault = tostring(Properties['message'])
| extend Source = tostring(Properties['source'])
| extend Action = tostring(Properties['action'])
| extend ExceptionStack = tostring(Properties['callstack'])
// | project ClientTimestamp, ExtensionVersion, ErrorMessage, Fault, ExceptionStack, Source, Action, VSCodeVersion, Platform, PlatformVersion, Properties

| project ServerTimestamp, ExtensionName, ExtensionVersion, FabricEnvironment, Fault, ExceptionStack, Source, Action, VSCodeSessionId, VSCodeVersion, Platform, VSCodeMachineId
| order by ServerTimestamp desc, VSCodeSessionId, ExtensionName desc

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/create"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")

{

};

RawEventsVSCodeExt
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric" or  ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric-functions"
//| where ExtensionVersion !has "placeholder" // temp
| where ServerTimestamp  between (['_startTime'] .. ['_endTime'])
| where iif(ExtensionName == 'fabric.vscode-fabric', (isempty(['_CoreVersion']) or ExtensionVersion in (_CoreVersion)), (isempty(['_UDFVersion']) or ExtensionVersion in (_UDFVersion)))
// todo
| extend FabricEnvironment = toupper(tostring(Properties['common.fabricenvironment']))
| where isempty(['_environment']) or FabricEnvironment in (['_environment']) // Multiple selection filtering
//
| extend ExtensionMode = toint(Properties['common.extensionmode']) // 1=prod, 2=dev, 3=test
| where ExtensionMode == 1 or ExtensionMode == 2
| extend IsMicrosoftInternal = toboolean(Properties['common.ismicrosoftinternal'])

cluster('https://DDTelvscode.kusto.windows.net').database('VSCode').RawEventsVSCode
| where ClientTimestamp between (['_startTime'] .. ['_endTime']) 
| where EventName == "monacoworkbench/extensiongallery:install"
| extend ExtensionId = tostring(Properties["id"])
| extend ExtensionName = tostring(Properties["name"])
| extend PublisherName = tostring(Properties["publishername"])
| extend ExtensionVersion = tostring(Properties["extensionversion"])
| extend PublisherDisplayName = tostring(Properties["publisherdisplayname"])
| extend VerificationStatus = tostring(Properties["verificationstatus"])
| extend QuerySource = tostring(Properties["querysource"])
| extend VSCodeVersion = tostring(Properties["version"])
| extend Platform = tostring(Properties["common.platform"])
| extend InstallSource = tostring(Properties["source"])
| where ExtensionId in ("fabric.vscode-fabric", "fabric.vscode-fabric-functions")
| project 
    ClientTimestamp,
    ExtensionId,
    ExtensionName,
    ExtensionVersion,
    VSCodeVersion,
    Platform,
    QuerySource,
    InstallSource,
    VerificationStatus,
    SessionId
| order by ClientTimestamp desc
